For jira API automation below are the basic need data and gothrough

JIRA rest doc :- https://docs.atlassian.com/software/jira/docs/api/REST/7.6.1/

we have used 
enum class -> load down all API end points
propert file -> Project name, issue ,user atached to 
UTILL class bind with excel
pojo serialization Deserialization

To install jira in local:- https://confluence.atlassian.com/adminjiraserver/installing-jira-applications-on-windows-938846835.html
it will be trial for 30 days once jira installation done start server 
if you are not able to start then look for service "Function Discovery Resource Publication" and start manually form control panel if alread working then stop and start jira again 

